articles.title: Trump withdraws Jared Isaacman’s nomination to lead NASA ‘after a thorough review of prior associations’ - CNN
articles.description: President Donald Trump on Saturday rescinded his nomination of tech billionaire Jared Isaacman to lead NASA, citing a “thorough review of prior associations.”
